  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Operation STEEL is a roguelike shoot-em-up rendered in hand-drawn art. Find and upgrade weapons while combatting the electronic legion across the galaxy!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489300/extras/bf9a91fc398e848f9a2628e374e29553.poster.avif?t=1745478086\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489300/extras/bf9a91fc398e848f9a2628e374e29553.webm?t=1745478086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489300/extras/bf9a91fc398e848f9a2628e374e29553.mp4?t=1745478086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated levels with randomised enemy waves and pickups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Branching paths - select from 20+ levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25+ weird and wonderful bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35+ unique weapons and items to find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your ship between levels at the shop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Rush mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awesome soundtrack by the amazing Dolphin!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489300/extras/f72bcef239468d794e3cbdaa5f3647f4.poster.avif?t=1745478086\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489300/extras/f72bcef239468d794e3cbdaa5f3647f4.webm?t=1745478086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489300/extras/f72bcef239468d794e3cbdaa5f3647f4.mp4?t=1745478086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
